# Welcome to **Hack2theFuture** 🚀  
A day of ideas, innovation, and irreverence — brought to you by *you*.  

This isn't just another workshop — it's a space to **co-create** tools, challenges, and hacks that make psychology more powerful, more practical, and way more fun.

---

## 🔍 Explore the Zones

::: {.zone-card}

![GoldBrains](images/StudentVoiceAwards.png){.zone-img}

### 🧠 GoldBrains  
[**Visit GoldBrains** →](GoldBrains.qmd)  
Celebrate the best of the staff and college — the *serious* and the *slightly weird* student-voted awards.
And suggest categories for student awards, maybe? If you want...

:::

::: {.zone-card}

![Weird Science Hack](images/WeirdScienceHack.png){.zone-img}

### 🧪 Weird Science Hack  
[**See what's in store** →](Hack2theFuture.qmd)  
Take control of your future in the department — ideas to make studying, socialising and researching weirder and more wonderful.

:::

::: {.zone-card}

![Breakout Club](images/BreakoutClub.png){.zone-img}

### 💥 BreakOut Club  
[**Join the BreakOut** →](BreakOutClub.qmd)  
It used to be the Breakfast Club - until we agreed we don't like mornings. See previous examples of student-led efforts to unlock their Psychology degree with skills, puzzles, publications, portfolios and pliers.

:::

::: {.zone-card}

![Arnie Says](images/ArniSays.png){.zone-img}

### 🤖 Arnie Says  
[**I am a cybernetic Psychologist, living tissue over metal endoskeleton** →](ArnieSays.qmd)  
We have teleported students from Year 2 and Year 3 to share their wisdom, hacks and tales of cunning. They will beam back insights to help you terminate the journey ahead.
And you can ask them anything via WooClap here https://app.wooclap.com/OZRLIY?from=instruction-slide event code OZRLIY at wooclap.com
:::

